specialAlerts.description: During 2019 we are renovating our building so we can deliver great, new hotel experiences. Disturbing noices may occur during this time but we welcome you to follow our transformation towards a hotel of tomorrow.
Between June 19th and July 1st our pool is closed due to unforeseen maintenance. Our relax, gym and sauna is open as per usual.
Until Oct 6 our jacuzzi is closed due to renovation.

The Slussen subway station outside our door is growing as a new bus terminal takes shape. This means that on weekdays guests at Scandic Sjöfartshotellet may hear blasting and feel vibrations from the construction work.
Between 11 - 18 August 2019 the hotel’s spa is closed due to maintenance.
Due to renovation, noise nuisances may occur in limited areas of the hotel until 18 August 2019.
We welcome kids to our hotel but unfortunately there is not enough space for extrabeds or a crib in our rooms. Therefore, at Scandic No. 53 kids always stay in the adult bed.

specialAlerts.title: closed due to total renovation
specialAlerts.description: The hotel is undergoing a total renovation and will be closed from 1st of September 2019 to 2nd of January 2020. See our other hotels in the area.
Between 18 August–27 September 2019 Spa Tropiclandia is closed due to maintenance.

specialAlerts.title: Renovation
specialAlerts.description: We are renovating and are sorry for the inconvenience this may cause.

specialAlerts.title: Please note
specialAlerts.description: Scandic Polar will open for winter season on 1 December 2019.
Scandic Falkoner will open 7 August 2019, but you can book your stay already now.
Due to a festival outside the hotel, it will be some noise in the periode 1 - 4 of August 2019.

specialAlerts.title: Seasonal hotel
specialAlerts.description: Scandic Honningsvåg is a seasonal hotel, and is closed between medio September and medio May. Scandic Bryggen, a charming boutique hotel with 42 rooms, located by the Honningsvåg port is open for reservations all year.
Due to maintenance of parts of the facade, there might be some noise in periods - we apology for the inconvenience.

We love kids but unfortunately there is not enough space for extrabeds or a crib in any of our rooms except Superior Family Four. Therefore, in all other rooms at Scandic Upplandsgatan kids always stay in adult's bed.
We are changing our elevators  and are sorry for the inconvenience this may cause. The work will be finished the 28th June.

specialAlerts.title: Scandic Sjølyst is expanding
specialAlerts.description: We have opened 223 newly renovated rooms. The hotel opens 2 new restaurants, bar and meeting rooms late summer/autumn 2019.

specialAlerts.title: Seasonal hotel
specialAlerts.description: Scandic Nordkapp is a seasonal hotel, and is closed between September and May. Scandic Bryggen, a charming boutique hotel with 42 rooms, located by the Honningsvåg port is open for reservations all year.
Due to maintenance of the roof, some noise may occur during the daytime from 10:00 to 16:00.
We close the pool until the beginning of July due to the renovation of the wardrobes.
From August 1st -16th 2019 we keep the Parkbadet closed due to renovation.
